{"tid":34130,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後沉迷「速食」文化，剪髮都要去速剪！咩心態","createTime":"2016-12-11T09:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T11:25:45.000Z","uid":19334,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8545dd109de04d4e8650cc35fd908162aaa0884e","tid":34130,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"話說今日星期日，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去左同男朋友拍拖拖，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小妹既男朋友做呀Sir，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個髮型就唔可以染，又唔可以太長，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以成日都會去飛髮鋪到剪短，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/hphotos-xaf1/t51.2885-15/e15/10983599_812792718796673_58220095_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.cdninstagram.com%2Fhphotos-xaf1%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe15%2F10983599_812792718796673_58220095_n.jpg&h=f2c67135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我成日都Suggest佢去剪刀敏俊個頭(如上圖)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為小妹覺得好charming，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢有d 同學開髮型鋪，就唔洗$800蚊咁貴，都係700鬆d(正價過千)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落街下果時，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到公司隻90後同事去街市果d 70蚊速剪，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻覺得佢成個人無哂品味，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連人靠衣裝呢d 基本禮儀都唔識，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更何況同佢講咩細味生活，享受人生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果去過1 d有質素小小既salon一定唔會去速剪囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平野邊有好野架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3400285b918ee0af5c2fc876448e8d0f7c43a55b","tid":34130,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好！d 90後真係成日貪快掛住速食 往往唔明果樣野本身既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b072d6ed9b6921aefb1524b3d31a121499ac63f5","tid":34130,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"90 後慳埋咁多都未買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8028854ecf9fcae44561cfa39f87151b8ee51d0","tid":34130,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"剪頭髮都好慳，90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, Ching Ho ball"},{"pid":"31002a6879608d4421abe640221db4d1cde8dc37","tid":34130,"uid":11314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"90後見到都眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b079779aed47c81ce6b9ceaa002f0e327d61a7df","tid":34130,"uid":12513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"你啲90後同事 成日比你撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, Ching hoball"},{"pid":"06de62e44d7976dc4a6324938e87a59b9f09cde6","tid":34130,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"90後真係冇得救"},{"pid":"0924c0b4b074405e95181e0e1fce47b1c21d04b8","tid":34130,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90後真係冇得救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牛ching 字字珠璣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擲地有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gi